            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》泡泡瑪特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09992:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09992\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09992-HK</a>)於2:18pm錄得1手21.52萬股交叉盤,每股造116.65元,較上日收市價低不足0.1%,涉資2510萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　泡泡瑪特現價無升跌,報116.7元;成交565.73萬股,成交金額6.72億元,主動買沽比率48:52,資金淨主動賣出2340萬元。(rw)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
