            "id": 5898975,
            "title": "《大手成交》騰訊一手約7萬股非自動對盤,涉資3481萬元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)於2:24pm錄得1手6.92萬股非自動對盤,每股造503元,較上日收市價低1.8%,涉資3481萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　騰訊現價跌1.7%,報503.5元;成交2137萬股,成交金額108.27億元,主動買沽比率40:60,資金淨主動賣出19.22億元。(rw)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
