            "title": "〈台股盤後〉一日反彈後 年線和2萬2大關又破防 尾盤遭摜殺跌316點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電今 (13) 日早盤重返千元大關，激勵大盤一度漲逾 200 點，不過盤中賣壓湧現，大盤由紅翻黑後一路下挫，尾盤爆量下殺，終場跌 316.68 點或 1.42%，以 21961.68 點作收，成交量 3652.56 億元。歷經昨天的一日反彈後，台股年線又失守，且 2 萬 2 整數關卡再度破防。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股今天大多臉黑，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 早盤重返千元大關後，盤中翻黑，終場跌 23 元，收 965 元，跌幅 2.33%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 都跌逾 1%。另外，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 及日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 也都臉綠，僅台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 小漲 0.26%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台塑四寶今天跌幅沈重，南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>) 跌逾半根停板，台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>)、台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 皆跌逾 3%，台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%。其他塑化個股也走弱，三芳 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1307:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1307\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1307-TW</a>)、亞聚 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1308-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，華夏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1305:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1305\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1305-TW</a>)、國喬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1312:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1312\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1312-TW</a>)、中石化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1314:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1314\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1314-TW</a>) 都有超過 2% 的跌幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IC 設計類股同樣走弱，旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)、晶豪科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3006:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3006\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3006-TW</a>)、敦泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3545:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3545\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3545-TW</a>)、晶相光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3530:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3530\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3530-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，瑞昱 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2379:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2379\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2379-TW</a>)、凌陽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2401:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2401\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2401-TW</a>)、偉詮電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2436:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2436\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2436-TW</a>)、揚智 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3041:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3041\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3041-TW</a>)、創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>) 則跌逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光學類股今天在大立光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3008:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3008\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3008-TW</a>) 走跌下，表現同樣弱勢。大立光跌逾半根停板，玉晶光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3406:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3406\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3406-TW</a>) 跌逾 4%，今國光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6209:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6209\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6209-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，先進光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3362:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3362\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3362-TW</a>)、揚明光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3504:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3504\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3504-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
